1. Open Terminal and go into the folder


cd /Users/rowan/helm-dashboard
2. Start the deploy


npx vercel
3. Answer its questions (just press Enter for most)

Set up and deploy? → press Enter (Yes)
Which scope? → press Enter
Link to existing project? → type n, press Enter
Project's name? → type the name you want, press Enter
Code directory? → press Enter (it's ./)
Modify settings? → type n, press Enter
4. Wait ~15 seconds. When it's done, it prints a link like:


https://your-name.vercel.app
